org.apache.ignite.compute.gridify.aop.aspectj

Class GridifySetToSetAspectJAspect

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.compute.gridify.aop.GridifySetToSetAbstractAspect
      • org.apache.ignite.compute.gridify.aop.aspectj.GridifySetToSetAspectJAspect

  • public class GridifySetToSetAspectJAspect
extends GridifySetToSetAbstractAspect
    AspectJ aspect that cross-cuts on all methods grid-enabled with GridifySetToSet annotation and potentially executes them on remote node.

    See GridifySetToSet documentation for more information about execution of gridified methods.

    See Also:
    GridifySetToSet
